title: Spectacular Slovakia #6: In Slovak spas, don’t worry when they call a doctor
itunes:author: The Slovak Spectator
itunes:summary: If you’re in need of some autumn relaxation, a visit to one of Slovakia’s many spas might give you just what you’re looking for. American travellers Don Stoll and Pat Alexy Stoll returned from a two-week-long trip around the country and have a lot of Slovak spa experiences to share in our latest podcast episode.
